high_descs: Go straight ahead to the right side of the white table.
Take the knife from the table that is next to the fork.
Turn right to face the black stand next to the end of the counter.
Cut the apple on the stand into pieces.
Go right to the counter to the left of the sink.
Put the knife in front of the salt.
Go left back to the black stand.
Take a piece of apple from the stand.
Go right to the sink.
Put the piece of apple in the sink to the left of the fork. Turn the water on then off. Take the apple out.
Go left back to the black stand.
Put the apple on the stand between the edge and the closest salt.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean piece of apple on a stand.

high_descs: Move forward to the front right corner of the table to the right of the range.
Pick up the knife with the gold handle to the right of the sponge and to the rear of the fork from the table.
Turn to the right and face the small table to the right of the trash bag in the corner.
Using the knife, slice the gold apple at the rear of the table and between the two salt shakers on the table.
Turn right and move toward the sink then turn left and face the counter area left of the sink.
Place the knife on the counter in front of the salt shaker.
Turn to the left, move toward the trash bag, then turn right and face the small table.
Pick up an apple slice from the sliced apple on the table.
Turn right, move to the sink, and then turn left to face the sink.
Place the apple slice in the front left corner of the sink to the left of the fork, rinse the apple slice using the faucet, then pick up the apple slice from the sink.
Turn left and move to the small table between the trash bag in the corner and the sink.
Place the apple slice in front of the center salt shaker and to the left of the tomato on the small table.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed apple slice on the table.

high_descs: Go forward to the large white table on the other side of the room.
Pick up the knife that is on the table.
Turn right to face the small black table.
Use the knife to slice the pear that is on the table.
Turn right and go the section of counter that is on the left of the sink.
Stick the knife into the counter, directly in front of the salt shaker.
Turn left and return to the small black table.
Pick up a slice of the pear.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Place the pear in the sink and run the faucet over it for a few seconds.
Turn left and return to the small black table.
Place the pear slice back on the small table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned pear slice on a small table.
